{"tid":40579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被告葉家銘（29歲）報稱為港大文學士一年級生","createTime":"2016-12-15T09:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T13:27:56.000Z","uid":7076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36743cc74eec6f7aef5e68447d6224a574b41e17","tid":40579,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"屢敗屢戰、在考了三次文憑試終如願以償入讀港大的29歲男生，聲稱因家人不願供他讀書，為自食其力支付學費，向九龍木球會提交偽造的推薦信，訛稱曾受僱於一間律師行任事務文員達6年，雖然後來受聘，惟最後被揭發說謊，男生今在裁判法院承認以欺騙手段取得金錢利益罪。<br />\n<br />\n被告葉家銘（29歲）報稱為港大文學士一年級生，求情稱已感到很後悔，是因為想自食其力以維持生活及支付學費而犯案，願向木球會賠償工作所得的10天工資及代通知金共逾3,900元。裁判官先索取被告的社會服務令報告，押後至本月29日判刑，並下令被告賠償該3,900多元予木球會，期間被告獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56051465&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56051465%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161215&d=HNQWM%2FSyCFwzJEfQzRQYdIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=2673cf73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56051465%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161215&h=2cc32f57\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56051465&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161215</a>"},{"pid":"0302a7eab826ce02f2402dee503092b84fd0a071","tid":40579,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"有loan借扮咩丫"},{"pid":"9c7921be7c089f548cd44acf356f86ebcd8d0a4d","tid":40579,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"廿九歲仲讀緊大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e58f4d96ac2e325452ea256969e7bec8b738a3d","tid":40579,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廿九歲仲讀緊大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl